## Overall

```{r}
top_players %>% 
  top_n(.ranksize, seasonPts) %>% 
  arrange(desc(seasonPts)) %>% 
  select(player=img, name, position, nflTeam, seasonPts, fantasyTeam=teamLogo) %>%
  knitr::kable()
```

